Supposed to be built in a train-based megabase.
import mostly basic resources, get science out (labs included).
even has stops included for importing of sciences not produced on nauvis.

has multiple stages of building, but if u want u can just build the last stage all at once


uses only t2 modules; no gleba stuff yet (havent bothered to go); will update with better parts later
title: 1.8K spm science mega-block
